INTRODUCING: The Preschool Chefs’ Club from @testkitchenkids! A themed monthly box program designed especially for 3-5 year olds. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Every month, kids receive a themed box filled with exclusive:⁠⁠
ATK kid-tested and kid-approved recipes (that are great for the whole family)⁠⁠
hands-on STEAM activities, games, and crafts⁠⁠
a unique illustrated storybook tied to the box theme⁠⁠
a grown-ups guide with a shopping list and additional resources for caregivers⁠⁠
plus other creative items (including stickers and a collectable achievement magnet) ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Link in profile to check out our first edition, Colors!
